title: Sound On: Manchin Holds Up Biden Agenda, VA Election

description:
Guests: Bill Hoagland, Senior Vice President at the Bipartisan Policy Institute, Amy Tarkanian, Republican Strategist and former Nevada state GOP chairwoman, Former Alaska Senator Mark Begich, Strategic Consulting Advisor at Brownstein Hyatt Farber Schreck, and Eric Wilson, managing partner of Startup Caucus.
